sentences: In September 2006, Azami's debut album Dunya was released by Awakening Records.
Previously he had featured as a backing vocalist on Sami Yusuf's first album, Al-Mu Ωallim.
In November 2006, he performed at the Global Peace and Unity Event at the ExCeL Exhibition Centre in London.
In 2013, after taking a five-year hiatus, Azami is due to return with a new music video and album under British record label UMA Global.
In July 2014, his single "Allahu" was released.
In August 2014, he was interviewed by Sunny and Shay Grewal on BBC London 94.9.
In July 2014, he performed at Eid in the Square.
